{"id": "1461791627864445140", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "這是一個純娛樂向，不講求幻夢高分速刷，純個人體驗靠手氣挑戰死裡逃生的娛樂組隊！\n第一次寫這種分享文可能很多細節不太清楚，甚至不知道這能不能算攻略請多多包涵。如過去已經有人發過相似隊伍純屬巧合，因為我沒有爬過所有攻略和組隊樓（\n將在留言區慢慢補上正文", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:38:02.858000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1461791628250452140", "filename": "IMG_5115.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 140738, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1461791627864445140/1461791628250452140/IMG_5115.png?ex=69cc148a&is=69cac30a&hm=04043ea44711ecd403ca8a58cf0540abbc344585e5c76d028d2f5060857e0b6b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461792655540228240", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "大佬們不怕扛傷，又或是一回合就能秒掉對手。但我是個小菜雞，看到對面打一下2000傷的敵人我就瑟瑟發抖。所以打牌只有一個原則:", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:42:07.875000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:42:33.067000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
