{"id": "1461793837528907930", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "純娛樂向所以命輪什麼的可以看自己覺得怎麼配合適就怎麼配，但我自己玩的習慣就是你至少要確保**足夠的黑印掉落能買造物，和每回合的銀鑰運轉是充足的**", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:46:49.683000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461794120623198239", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為這一隊要能做到不停的降傷很大一部分要靠鑰令幫忙", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:47:57.178000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461795223310041192", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "貼一下最近一局但我真的打得很爛，主打一個安全牌，但凡噴一次死扛都是對膽小鬼的不尊重（X", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T18:52:20.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1461795222966112499", "filename": "IMG_5111.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1181244, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1461791627864445140/1461795222966112499/IMG_5111.png?ex=69cc17e3&is=69cac663&hm=abbd88309572efd6bdd1043db6d0ec3133554920d1a13973a69dd84944aafdcf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461798220413014261", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "【核心思路】\n這一隊的核心主要就是集中在塔微、皮克曼和鑰令的三人轉上。\n皮克曼的四費蝕骨色彩除了能攻擊全體還附帶偷取力量，因此在面對一群令人絕望的小怪時有時能起到非常良好的保命手段。\n同時這張牌十分有意思的機制就是當同回合使用**發現**的時候算力就會減一，但現在發現這機制在整個遊戲裡可以說是少之又少，其中兩個還是在鑰令上。\n# 但是\n我們的塔微娘娘正好就是目前全遊戲裡除了皮克曼自己以外，招式裡唯一有發現的角色。", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T19:04:14.644000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1461798219578343768", "filename": "IMG_5116.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 822632, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1461791627864445140/1461798219578343768/IMG_5116.png?ex=69cc1aae&is=69cac92e&hm=9bcd247560cff66ed6248970075fd698e3a806766d710ec7df2b6eec7db7dc62&"}, {"id": "1461798220140380260", "filename": "IMG_5117.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 290605, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1461791627864445140/1461798220140380260/IMG_5117.png?ex=69cc1aae&is=69cac92e&hm=7fc8f91e1454e1f03843fb9e6143c8df611e02a26a3b9518ea5c8898dc0bda65&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461801411149955295", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "因此我們在這裡其實可以看到一個非常正向的循環\n1. 皮克曼自帶2次發現（繪影摹型1次，狂氣爆發1次。皮克曼有三啟的話有時候狂氣爆發還能再多一次）\n2. 塔微1次發現\n3.鑰令選擇有發現效果的1次", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T19:16:55.375000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461803672294920405", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "這樣看來的話算是不多不少的四次。\n但是，又一次但是\n我們的塔微娘娘可是能從隊伍所屬界域「發現」牌的，也就是說，她是有機會能開大開出皮克曼的繪影摹型和蝕骨色彩的。\n這下我們的發現和減傷保證又再+1，算上塔微開完大之後的第一張牌能發動兩次的話，接著打出她的繪影摹型甚至能直接發現+2", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T19:25:54.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-16T19:29:21.829000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1461803672253235220", "filename": "IMG_5098.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1239046, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1461791627864445140/1461803672253235220/IMG_5098.png?ex=69cc1fc2&is=69cace42&hm=da7734371d6c10b605c42f75d6ec6dbabf3265efc829a1e056b6ec261e163c3b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1461807743005364324", "channel_id": "1461791627864445140", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212395834029641778", "author_name": "carrot_chicken", "author_bot": false, "content": "【輔助的選擇】\n\n兩位陪跑這裡我選了萊克和阿格里帕（蜘蛛）。\n蜘蛛我是之前融災時沒人能用才陰錯陽差塞進來的。用久了之後覺得她的上護盾能力還有胚胎運轉速度還行，再加上還能上毒多了一層輸出。\n但她可以換成任何一位胚胎手！尤其是羊媽，用羊媽的話整體輸出應該會更上一層。但蜘蛛是打融災時沒人能塞的好選擇。", "timestamp": "2026-01-16T19:42:05.007000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-17T06:24:17.980000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1461791627864445140", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "諸君，我喜歡抽牌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174180524034637854"]}
